# ALL_CAPS filename convention: working files go in ALL_CAPS, research uses
# lowercase. Catches the whole class (SESSION_STATE, MORNING_BRIEFING, etc.)
# without per-file blocklists. Standards (README, LICENSE, CHANGELOG) and
# known canonical research (ADAPTER_PLAYBOOK, UNSLOTH_RECIPE) are whitelisted.
[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]*.md
!README.md
!LICENSE
!LICENSE.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
# Tsunami skills are canonical workflow blueprints — track them
!tsunami/skills/**/SKILL.md
!tsunami/skills/**/WAVEFORM.md

